{This move is fairly unusual, but you may see it.} exd5 9. dxc5 Bxc5 {This is an 
isolated queen's pawn position. White has a solid position, but not very many 
chances. Black can develop comfortably.} *

[Event "Nimzo-Indian Defense- Tournament Edition"]
