1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nc3 Bb4 4. Qb3 c5 5. Nf3 {White can also try this natural 
developing move.} b6 {Black aims to fianchetto his light-squared bishop.} 6. a3 
Bxc3+ 7. Qxc3 O-O {Black has very little to worry about and can comfortably 
fianchetto his bishop.} *

